  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "The second half of the Soul Drinkers' arc, collected: the Ork-invasion of Vanqualis and the chapter-civil-war that splits the brothers between renegade-loyalist and openly Chaotic; the flight to the galactic rim where the Necrons stir and the Mechanicus pursues; and at last the Imperial Fists' capture of the chapter and the trial aboard the Phalanx, where Daenyathos's centuries-long corruption-scheme comes home and Sarpedon's tale ends. Three novels and short fiction in one volume — the slow disintegration of a chapter that chose rebellion.",
